name: Baked Car II
description:
Had a car crash accident for the very first time in my life six years ago. Got our car repaired and repainted in this big car workshop. I was so fascinated by the whole process and surroundings as it was, too, my first time experiencing such sightings. This is the closer look to the inside of my previous piece "Baked Car I".

Captured and edited with my 2015 ASUS Zenfone 4 - A400CG Android phone.
